        System.out.println(new Solution().findAnagrams("", ""));
    }

    public List<Integer> findAnagrams(String s, String p) {
        List<Integer> rstList = new ArrayList<>();
        char[] compArr = p.toCharArray();

        Arrays.sort(compArr);

        for (int i = 0; i <= s.length() - compArr.length; i++) {
            char[] targetArr = s.substring(i, i + compArr.length).toCharArray();

            Arrays.sort(targetArr);

            if (Arrays.hashCode(compArr) == Arrays.hashCode(targetArr)) {
                rstList.add(i);
            }
        }

        return rstList;
    }
}
